name: BEYOND ALL RECKONING CD
description:
IT'S HERE.

Aggressor's highly anticipated new studio album, "Beyond All Reckoning", is finally here. Delivered in a slick and eco-friendly digipack, the album features nine new songs and a running time of almost fifty minutes! 

"galloping tempos, duelling guitars, gruff vocals, and groove... the thing about Beyond All Reckoning that stands out the most is that no matter how fast and heavy the songs get, there is an obvious groove to everything" - Hellbound.ca review 

Track listing:
1. What Is Me
2. Justice Lost
3. Staring Down At You
4. More To Discover
5. Unknown
6. The Wanderer
7. Unto The World
8. I Am The Locust
9. Redemption (First Eyes Awake)

There is a limited supply of autographed copies of "Beyond All Reckoning" available on a first come first serve basis - just choose which version of the CD you would like from the drop down menu above the "add to cart" button

name: LOGO PATCH
description: From the vault! 4.5x10" cloth patch featuring the original Pure Canadian Aggression logo (red on black) and website address. These oldschool as fuck patches have each been handcut by a member of the band...DIY! Cut em up, stitch em on, and wear it proud!
